cc:Work.dc:description:
A Gridfinity box for drills or similar tools
You need to add a hole pattern to all horizontal layers except the very bottom
Created with Boxes.py (https://boxes.hackerspace-bamberg.de/) Command line: boxes GridfinityDrillBox Command line short: boxes GridfinityDrillBox
